{"word":"ἀλίμενος","slug":"ἀλίμενος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀλίμενος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:λιμήν'><el>λιμήν</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>without harbour, harbourless</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>without shelter, inhospitable</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}